info.name: FAO WCA Crop List published as RDF/SKOS(XKOS/DCAT) (v2.1, draft)
info.description: This is the Simple Knowledge Organization System (SKOS) derived from the FAO WCA Crop List. The FAO WCA Crop List was developed for the 2010 round of agricultural censuses. The version represented here is an experimental conversion (into RDF/SKOS), and should not be used as a reference. See original dataset matadata at http://stats-class.fao.uniroma2.it/caliper-catalog/dataset/WCACROPS
